snippet.title: Mario Forever: Community Edition - Release
snippet.description:
Mario Forever makes a return with a more polished look, flexible settings and new custom elements! Created on Thunder Engine, Mario Forever: Community Edition aims to bring both the classic feel of the game and bring a lot of quality of life features and cosmetics, not seen before, to the game.

More info & Download: https://mfce.rnx.su/
Alternative download link: https://file.marioforever.net/Mario%20Forever/%E5%9B%BD%E5%A4%96%E4%BD%9C%E5%93%81/Meteo%20Dream
